{"title":"QUOC Introduces Escape Road Lace","link":"https://theradavist.com/quoc-introduces-escape-road-lace/","date":1712845133000,"content":"<p><em>UK-based brand <a href=\"https://quoc.cc/en-us\" target=\"_blank\">QUOC</a> adds to their Escape line with the just-launched Escape Road Lace. Find all the specs from QUOC below…<span></span></em></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Side.jpg?fit=1200%2C4800&amp;quality=75&amp;resize=6605,4926&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Side.jpg?w=6605&amp;quality=75 6605w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Side.jpg?resize=1200,895&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Side.jpg?resize=2000,1492&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Side.jpg?resize=768,573&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Side.jpg?resize=1536,1146&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Side.jpg?resize=2048,1527&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Side.jpg?fit=1200%2C4800&amp;quality=75&amp;resize=6605,4926&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Side.jpg?w=6605&amp;quality=75 6605w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Side.jpg?resize=1200,895&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Side.jpg?resize=2000,1492&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Side.jpg?resize=768,573&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Side.jpg?resize=1536,1146&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Side.jpg?resize=2048,1527&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The Escape Road Lace takes the comfort and performance of the dial shoe and combines it with an elegant, laced aesthetic. With a carbon composite outsole that optimally balances stiffness and comfort, this ultra-distance road shoe is not sensitive to the odd section of unpredictable terrain. The lightweight, streamlined silhouette is primed for miles of exploration, while malleable heel padding and a foot-hugging fit delivers all-day comfort. Built for the all-weather weekend cyclist whose ultimate end game is an enjoyable ride, QUOC’s Escape Road range represents an end to tiptoeing around worrying about scratches and scuffs. A favorite among those who value style, the lace system allows for reliability on long rides and offers even pressure distribution across the top of the foot. and well-positioned airflow ventilation holes ensure a breathable ride that bridges climates and seasons.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Overhead.jpg?fit=1200%2C4800&amp;quality=75&amp;resize=6605,4926&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Overhead.jpg?w=6605&amp;quality=75 6605w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Overhead.jpg?resize=1200,895&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Overhead.jpg?resize=2000,1492&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Overhead.jpg?resize=768,573&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Overhead.jpg?resize=1536,1146&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_Black_Overhead.jpg?resize=2048,1527&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Overhead.jpg?fit=1200%2C4800&amp;quality=75&amp;resize=6605,4926&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Overhead.jpg?w=6605&amp;quality=75 6605w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Overhead.jpg?resize=1200,895&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Overhead.jpg?resize=2000,1492&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Overhead.jpg?resize=768,573&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Overhead.jpg?resize=1536,1146&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/QUOC_Escape-Road-Lace_White_Overhead.jpg?resize=2048,1527&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Specifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Weight: 255g (EU42, one shoe)</li>\n<li>Size range: EU38-47 (whole sizes)</li>\n<li>Available in White and Black colorways</li>\n<li>Sole: Carbon Composite</li>\n<li>Upper: PU</li>\n<li>Double lock, anti-slip laces for multi-point adjustment</li>\n<li>Malleable heel padding and supportive, foot-hugging fit</li>\n<li>Organically structured ventilation air holes for breathability</li>\n<li>Reflective zig-zag detailing lace-guide</li>\n<li>Replaceable Heel Pad</li>\n<li>3-bolt road cleat compatible (Look/Speedplay)</li>\n<li>MSRP: £130 GBP | $180 USD | €160 EUR</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://quoc.cc/en-us\" target=\"_blank\">QUOC</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/quoc-introduces-escape-road-lace/\">QUOC Introduces Escape Road Lace</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"Hailey Moore","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"ab4257744021b289758e61e07cc2077a6da880adc201a1cfa337e2457b7497e9","category":"Cycling"}